text: La otra y yo, also known as The Other and Me in English, is a 1949 Argentine comedy movie. It is directed by Antonio Momplet and starring Amelia Bence, Enrique Alvarez Diosdado, Fernando Lamas, Mercedes Simone. ==Other websites== * Category:1949 comedy movies Category:Argentine comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Antonio Momplet
title: La otra y yo
